&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for someone who brings enthusiasm, precision, and a “let’s get this done” mindset. If you excel at staying organized in a fast‑moving environment, love coordinating across teams, and take pride in keeping every detail sharp and on track, you’ll shine here. If you’re energized by juggling multiple priorities, connecting people and information, and building systems that help a mission‑driven team thrive, this role will feel like home..&lt;/p&gt;
