&lt;li&gt;Draft, edit, and proofread donor-facing materials (acknowledgments, stewardship letters, proposals, reports).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support annual giving, donor stewardship, revenue campaigns, and board engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain internal fundraising timelines and follow-up systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Cross‑Borough Coordination and Borough Event Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
